Deploy a LAMP server

--> Linux OS
Update your system by running 
sudo dnf update

--> Apache web server
Install Apache HTTPD in RHEL 8: sudo dnf install httpd

--> MySQL or MariaDB server to store data
Set up MariaDB (MySQL clone) on RHEL 8 sudo dnf install mariadb-server

--> PHP for a server-side dynamic web generation programming language
Finally install PHP 7.x to complete a LAMP set up on RHEL 8, run sudo dnf install @php

Test your LAMP setup
